snippet.title: F2OGGY TRAILER
snippet.description:
Game trailer and intro for F2OGGY (Only One Survives!)
F2OGGY (Only one survives!) is a local multiplayer Brute-Force Frog-Combat Simulator™ made for a growing audience of competitive frogfans.
The game is downloadable here: https://juegosrancheros.itch.io/fantastic-arcade-2016
